# 🏥 Vox Connect AI  
### Smart Triage for Clinics & Community Health Centers

---

## 🔍 Problem

- Long queues and overwhelmed staff  
- Patients misdirected or misunderstood  
- Delays in diagnosis and reduced care quality

---

## 💡 Solution

- AI-powered kiosk for autonomous patient intake  
- Uses NLP and machine learning to predict illness  
- Operates offline with voice and multilingual support

---

## 🎯 Objectives

- ⏱️ Faster patient processing  
- 🎯 Accurate triage and referral  
- 🏥 Scalable deployment  
- 📊 Better public health data

---

## 🧠 How It Works

1. Patient inputs symptoms (text or voice)  
2. NLP extracts key terms and duration  
3. ML model predicts illness  
4. System refers patient to correct room  
5. Logs data for planning and retraining

---

## 🔊 Features

- Chatbot/Softbot interface  
- Speech recognition & synthesis  
- Multilingual support (English, isiZulu, Afrikaans)  
- Offline-ready hardware (Raspberry Pi, Jetson Nano)

---

## 📈 Impact

- Reduced wait times  
- Improved diagnosis accuracy  
- Inclusive, scalable healthcare access
